":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"所以支共真係好好笑<br />\n係要做到咁肉酸<br />\n其實只要參選人必須全部經由選委會篩選完<br />\n揀乾揀淨先可以參選<br />\n已經達到晒佢哋控制議會嘅目的<br />\n又可以繼續扮香港有選舉<br />\n根本無必要刻意搞一堆選委會委任嘅位出嚟<br />\n依家變成大部分議席變相係政府委任<br />\n少部份民選議席都要經過政府篩選<br />\n即係講到味都係政府委任<br />\n嗰種「明明已經無選舉，但刻意要扮到仲有選舉」嘅柒味出晒嚟<br />\n好似荒死人唔知係扮<br />\n就好似一個超肥肥婆刻意要着三點式俾人睇自己身材咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d209be90bbf2428d30b1fb45b1480a96ec6d68","tid":2450161,"uid":298796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"0直選啦, 講經咩<br />\n以後建制泛民都無直選, SUPER<br />\n<br />\n邊個奶共邊個做, 最公平"},{"pid":"762a83e97161404c047de4bf17d45ecf71a61c4c","tid":2450161,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35d4fb41c7b1dde7da29c99647838bb21b3144cd","tid":2450161,"uid":61589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6580af37f8700fddbfda6672e90706625ce71561","tid":2450161,"uid":179409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"等同變晒委任制分餅仔<br />\n仲選乜嘢舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"分俾止驚党班新腥港人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地已經諗住淘汰堆忠誠的廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"擺明condom仔啦 唔係以為自己一世無憂呀？"},{"pid":"f44d6d9b686d616c7122d197489106475278209d","tid":2450161,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711eb8cd877f85a06276a7151ece4bbbaaf9b9d4","tid":2450161,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"中國搞殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i